In case of a tie, this market will resolve in favor of the tied athlete representing USA. If no tied athlete represents USA, or if both tied athletes represent USA, this market will resolve in favor of the athlete whose last name comes first in alphabetical order.

The resolution source will be the first official results published by the International Olympic Committee (IOC).

title: Will Obama endorse Kamala by tomorrow?

markets.question: Will Obama endorse Kamala by tomorrow?
markets.description:
This market will resolve to "Yes" if Barack Obama announces that he formally endorses Kamala Harris as Democratic Nominee for President of the United States by July 26, 11:59 PM ET. Otherwise this market will resolve to "No".

If Obama endorses another candidate for Democratic Nominee, this market will resolve to "No".

The resolution source for this market will be official information from Barack Obama or one of his representatives.
